st_touched":1654705220,"title":"现在买 Mac mini 会不会年底被背刺","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858089","created":1654654540,"deleted":0,"content":"感觉今年的 m2 比 M1 性能并没有提高多少，不想等了，studio 又贼贵。 年底出 M1 PRO,或 M2 pro mini 铁定被背刺，纠结","content_rendered":"<p>感觉今年的 m2 比 M1 性能并没有提高多少，不想等了，studio 又贼贵。 年底出 M1 PRO,或 M2 pro mini 铁定被背刺，纠结</p>\n","last_modified":1654654540,"replies":54,"id":858089},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991","name":"iphone","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991","title":"iPhone","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":9409,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":"iPhone","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","stars":2892,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":8,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"id":430910,"username":"justNoBody","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/justNoBody","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aaa04c58b2ee20740098a1b72d186b2a?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aaa04c58b2ee20740098a1b72d186b2a?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/aaa04c58b2ee20740098a1b72d186b2a?s=73&d=retro","created":1563692658,"last_modified":1654070529},"last_reply_by":"wazggcd","last_touched":1654700921,"title":"最近突然意识到通话录音这个功能还是挺重要的， iPhone 真的没有办法实现么？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858170","created":1654668161,"deleted":0,"content":"目前 iPhone 据我所知有几种方案：\r\n1. 越狱：\r\n\t- 优点：软件直接支持，简单；\r\n    - 缺点：\r\n    \t- 越狱很难，需要特定版本；\r\n        - 越狱以后，系统不太稳定，很多 app 会检测手机是否越狱（虽然有反监测插件，但总有疏漏）；\r\n2. 通过支持录音的耳机录音：\r\n\t- 优点：想不出来\r\n        - 缺点：\r\n\t\t- 得多带一根耳机，打电话之前得换一下\r\n\t\t- 紧急情况下，这个方法可能因为自己身体原因无法更换耳机，或者没时间更换而导致用不上\r\n3. 外放，使用其他设备录音；\r\n\t- 优点：想不出来\r\n    - 缺点：\r\n    \t- 得多带一台设备（可以是 apple watch ）\r\n        - 可能需要周围没有陌生人？\r\n        - 紧急情况下，这个方法可能因为自己身体原因无法另外开启录音，或者没时间开启而导致用不上\r\n        \r\n我目前就是在用 apple watch ，但是只是针对部分电话，且我具备安静的环境时，才会这样，否则还是不录音。\r\n\r\n请教各位，有没有什么巧妙的方法，可以透露一下，或者讨论一下可行性之类的？","content_rendered":"<p>目前 iPhone 据我所知有几种方案：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n越狱：<ul>\n<li>优点：软件直接支持，简单；</li>\n<li>\n缺点：<ul>\n<li>越狱很难，需要特定版本；</li>\n<li>越狱以后，系统不太稳定，很多 app 会检测手机是否越狱（虽然有反监测插件，但总有疏漏）；</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n通过支持录音的耳机录音：<ul>\n<li>\n优点：想不出来<ul>\n<li>缺点：</li>\n<li>得多带一根耳机，打电话之前得换一下</li>\n<li>紧急情况下，这个方法可能因为自己身体原因无法更换耳机，或者没时间更换而导致用不上</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n外放，使用其他设备录音；<ul>\n<li>优点：想不出来</li>\n<li>\n缺点：<ul>\n<li>得多带一台设备（可以是 apple watch ）</li>\n<li>可能需要周围没有陌生人？</li>\n<li>紧急情况下，这个方法可能因为自己身体原因无法另外开启录音，或者没时间开启而导致用不上</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>我目前就是在用 apple watch ，但是只是针对部分电话，且我具备安静的环境时，才会这样，否则还是不录音。</p>\n<p>请教各位，有没有什么巧妙的方法，可以透露一下，或者讨论一下可行性之类的？</p>\n","last_modified":1654668297,"replies":51,"id":858170},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_large.png?m=1605263518","name":"browsers","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_normal.png?m=1605263518","title":"浏览器","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/browsers","topics":525,"footer":"","header":"","title_alternative":"Browsers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_mini.png?m=1605263518","stars":298,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":422,"parent_node_name":"software"},"member":{"id":583228,"username":"a33","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/a33","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7882/9110/583228_mini.png?m=1654160777","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7882/9110/583228_normal.png?m=1654160777","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7882/9110/583228_large.png?m=1654160777","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7882/9110/583228_xlarge.png?m=1654160777","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7882/9110/583228_xlarge.png?m=1654160777","avatar